{"TopicId":199334,"ForumId":109,"TopicTitle":"May I suggest a Light Switch in the VAB?","CreatedByName":"MantoF18","CreatedById":209218,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-01-05T05:30:04Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"MantoF18","CreatedById":209218,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-01-05T05:30:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHello,\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m a fan of KSP.\u00A0 Sometimes when I\u0027m making a new ship and adding my lights on it, I think... \u0022What will this look like the the darkness of space?\u0022\u00A0 Can we have an option the turn off the lights in the Vehicle Assembly Building and or the space hanger while under construction?\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThank\u00A0you for KSP and thanks for your consideration,\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMantoF18\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222021-01-07T06:08:05Z\u0022 title=\u002201/07/2021 06:08  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EJanuary 7, 2021\u003C/time\u003E by MantoF18\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gargamel","CreatedById":64714,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-01-05T06:13:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHey, \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/209218-mantof18/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022209218\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/209218-mantof18/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@MantoF18\u003C/a\u003E, there\u2019s a mod for that in KSP already, I believe it\u2019s called \u201CLights Out\u201D. \u00A0Might fit\u00A0the bill until they make it stock, if they ever do. \u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222021-01-05T09:05:31Z\u0022 title=\u002201/05/2021 09:05  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EJanuary 5, 2021\u003C/time\u003E by Gargamel\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Guest","CreatedById":-1,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-01-05T06:20:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWelcome to the forums \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/209218-mantof18/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022209218\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/209218-mantof18/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@MantoF18\u003C/a\u003E! Glad to see you here! I think that would also be a cool idea. Never really thought of that before. The more I think about it the more cool of an idea it\u00A0seems to be.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-01-05T19:36:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes, it\u0027s a bother to have to take a craft to the launch pad and warp to night time to see what it will look like. \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/kerbal-forum-uploads/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"VoidCosmos","CreatedById":192336,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-01-06T13:31:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHm.... Dark Mode you say?\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThats a good idea\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"steve_v","CreatedById":69272,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-01-06T13:47:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPersonally I think Lights Out, Editor Extensions, and \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003ERCS\u003C/abbr\u003E Build Aid should all be stock construction scene features. I\u0027m not going to hold my breath though, considering how it took to get a stripped down \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Engineer Redux (mod)\u0022\u003EKER\u003C/abbr\u003E into the game.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"OvinandRusk","CreatedById":206785,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-01-06T22:45:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nthat could be cool\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Commodore_32","CreatedById":200414,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-01-06T22:49:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAn addition to this suggestion should be that with the lights, it also toogles their CPU heavy particles, so we can push the FPS to the max!!!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MantoF18","CreatedById":209218,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-01-07T06:06:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHey everyone,\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks for the positive comments and feedback.\u00A0 Garmamel, I appreciate you mentioning the Mod, I will be checking it out for certain.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMantoF18\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}